{"id":150187,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/噁-深圳污水製饅頭-日賣千個/","date":"2011-05-06T10:00:55Z","modified":"2011-05-06T10:00:55Z","title":"噁 深圳污水製饅頭 日賣千個","content":"<p><a href=\"http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33368280/IssueID/20110506/pvtype/r\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20110506/33368280_577d72c472419d5779d7ea81c731677c_120x120.jpg\" /></a><br />【大陸中心╱綜合外電報導】中國廣東省深圳市與重慶市，日前又陸續傳出多起駭人聽聞的「黑心食品」。包括地下工廠竟以廢棄水井內的污水，混合化學膨鬆劑製成廉價饅頭、或是無照工廠以豬皮包裹豬肉凍後再以棉線綑綁，製作出亞硝酸鹽含量超標的致癌「假豬腳」，甚至還有火鍋店被查獲以福馬林泡毛肚保鮮。 </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33368280/IssueID/20110506/pvtype/r\">詳全文：噁 深圳污水製饅頭 日賣千個</a><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://rss.feedsportal.com/c/33277/f/585303/s/14a103bc/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%99%81+%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E8%A3%BD%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD+%E6%97%A5%E8%B3%A3%E5%8D%83%E5%80%8B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.nextmedia.com%2Fapplenews%2Farticle%2Fart_id%2F33368280%2FIssueID%2F20110506%2Fpvtype%2Fr\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%99%81+%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E8%A3%BD%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD+%E6%97%A5%E8%B3%A3%E5%8D%83%E5%80%8B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.nextmedia.com%2Fapplenews%2Farticle%2Fart_id%2F33368280%2FIssueID%2F20110506%2Fpvtype%2Fr\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091408019/u/0/f/585303/c/33277/s/14a103bc/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091408019/u/0/f/585303/c/33277/s/14a103bc/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/t